{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kero Quest 64 is a <i>Collectathon 3D Platformer</i> inspired by other games in the genre, especially those from the late 90s. You take control of Kero, a blue frog seeking to stop a prince from abusing his newly gained powers by collecting Magical Shards around the kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411900/extras/moves.gif?t=1738177830\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Big World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you must find your way through <strong>20+ Open Levels</strong>, each with its own retro 3D aesthetic. On your quest to gain Magical Shards, you will collect various things such as <strong>Gold Coins</strong> and <strong>Costumes</strong> for Kero to wear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411900/extras/course-1.gif?t=1738177830\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple controls with some advanced movement options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple, light-hearted story that can be enjoyed by anyone.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro graphics inspired by the late 90s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 20 levels to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A variety of things to collect in every level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optional content such as costumes to unlock.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411900/extras/grappling-hook.gif?t=1738177830\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738177830","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411900/page.bg.j